<paragraph blockId="5.[136,1452,1062,1192]" pageId="5" pageNumber="76">
Valve linear, 82–92 µm long, 5.5–6.0 µ wide, transverse striae circa 
<quantity box="[814,900,1062,1084]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.699" metricValueMax="4.826" metricValueMin="4.572" pageId="5" pageNumber="76" unit="in" value="18.5" valueMax="19.0" valueMin="18.0">18–19 in</quantity>
10 µm, longitudinal striae circa 
<quantity box="[1225,1312,1062,1084]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.144" metricValueMax="9.398" metricValueMin="8.89" pageId="5" pageNumber="76" unit="in" value="36.0" valueMax="37.0" valueMin="35.0">35–37 in</quantity>
10 µm, raphe sternum staff-shaped in its apical portion.
</paragraph>
